This might be part of his plan.

168
00:09:02,486 --> 00:09:03,719
‐Mum Mew and Gobi: His plan?

169
00:09:03,752 --> 00:09:05,619
‐Yes, there's seven of them.

170
00:09:05,652 --> 00:09:07,452
