and he's waiting
for the right moment.

172
00:09:10,586 --> 00:09:13,052
‐Mum Mew: I see.
‐Gobi: Good plan.

173
00:09:13,086 --> 00:09:17,219
‐Shogun: The most important
battle technique
is the hardest to achieve,

174
00:09:17,252 --> 00:09:18,852
mastering one's mind.

175
00:09:18,886 --> 00:09:21,186
