186
00:09:49,619 --> 00:09:51,252
‐(Shogun laughing)

187
00:09:54,252 --> 00:09:56,252
(clears throat)
Now, onto the next maneuver.

188
00:09:56,286 --> 00:09:57,686
‐Mum Mew: I don't think
he has any plan.

189
00:09:57,719 --> 00:10:00,219
He's just trying
to get to know that girl.

190
00:10:00,252 --> 00:10:02,652
‐(all grunting)

191
00:10:11,219 --> 00:10:13,119
‐Tiger: Huh?
‐All: Huh?

192
00:10:16,552 --> 00:10:18,452
‐That Zuum stole my bag.

193
00:10:18,486 --> 00:10:22,686
‐Catch him!
‐No, Holly, stay here with me.

194
00:10:22,719 --> 00:10:25,152
‐Gobi: Halt.
‐Huh? How dare you!

195
00:10:27,419 --> 00:10:28,852
Oh.

196
00:10:28,886 --> 00:10:31,586
