I'm after?

197
00:10:32,786 --> 00:10:35,119
You mean‐‐
‐Gobi: Uh‐huh. Uh‐huh.

198
00:10:35,152 --> 00:10:36,352
‐Shogun: Hmm.

199
00:10:41,886 --> 00:10:43,052
Very sly indeed.

200
00:10:43,086 --> 00:10:45,886
But there's no fooling
Shogun the mighty.

201
00:10:45,919 --> 00:10:48,086
