the minute I saw them.

202
00:10:48,119 --> 00:10:49,819
‐You did not know!

203
00:10:49,852 --> 00:10:53,352
‐(yells) How dare they
take advantage of my goodwill?

204
00:10:53,386 --> 00:10:57,486
