Shogun the mighty will
teach them a lesson!

205
00:10:57,519 --> 00:11:00,086
‐Tiger: That Zuum
will think twice next time
he tries to steal something.

206
00:11:00,119 --> 00:11:01,952
‐Holly: Maybe we were
too hard on him.

207
00:11:01,986 --> 00:11:04,586
‐He's gotta learn that
crime just doesn't pay.

208
00:11:04,619 --> 00:11:06,052
‐Stealing no good.

209
00:11:06,086 --> 00:11:09,719
‐(groaning) Please help me,
Mum Mew.

210
00:11:10,786 --> 00:11:13,052
‐Huh? Where's Shogun?

211
00:11:13,086 --> 00:11:16,086
‐Mocchi: Not here‐chi.
‐Hare: He took off on us!

212
00:11:16,119 --> 00:11:19,086
‐Talk about nerve. You'd think
he could've said goodbye first.

213
00:11:19,119 --> 00:11:22,319
‐I was hoping
he could stick around
and train us some more.

214
00:11:22,352 --> 00:11:24,719
‐Yeah. Me, too.

215
00:11:24,752 --> 00:11:26,619
‐Wait. I can sense him nearby.

216
00:11:28,319 --> 00:11:33,652
‐Shogun: So, you are
the seven veteran warriors
united as a single force.

217
00:11:33,686 --> 00:11:37,052
‐What do you mean,
"seven veteran warriors
united as one"?

218
00:11:37,086 --> 00:11:38,252
‐Never heard of 'em.

219
00:11:38,286 --> 00:11:42,619
‐And on that note,
why don't we drop the subject
and get back to our training?

220
00:11:42,652 --> 00:11:45,552
‐(laughing) I have discovered
your true identity

221
00:11:45,586 --> 00:11:47,619
