fight us for, Shogun?
We are your friends.

224
00:11:51,819 --> 00:11:54,552
‐We just wanna train with you.
We're not looking
for any battles.

225
00:11:54,586 --> 00:11:57,352
‐Shogun: You tried to steal
my invincible battle techniques.

226
00:11:57,386 --> 00:12:00,086
